happy to take a bit more risk in the hope of potentially

18
00:01:28.440 --> 00:01:32.050
higher returns, hopefully there'll be a fund
to match your needs.

19
00:01:32.050 --> 00:01:37.789
I hope you found that helpful – but there is a lot more
information about Ready-made Investments on our website.

